有研究認為[[密毛犰狳|密毛犰狳]]很可能只是[[長毛犰狳|長毛犰狳]]的指名亞種的異名，而整個[[毛犰狳属|毛犰狳属]]亦很可能是一個[[多系群|多系群]]<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Abba|first=Agustín M.|last2=Cassini|first2=Guillermo H.|last3=Valverde|first3=Guido|last4=Tilak|first4=Marie-Ka|last5=Vizcaíno|first5=Sergio F.|last6=Superina|first6=Mariella|last7=Delsuc|first7=Frédéric|date=2015-08-03|title=Systematics of hairy armadillos and the taxonomic status of the Andean hairy armadillo (Chaetophractus nationi)|url=https://academic.oup.com/jmammal/article/96/4/673/846208|journal=Journal of Mammalogy|volume=96|issue=4|pages=673–689|doi=10.1093/jmammal/gyv082|issn=0022-2372|access-date=2018-03-18|archive-date=2018-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180604112250/https://academic.oup.com/jmammal/article/96/4/673/846208|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last=Gibb|first=Gillian C.|last2=Condamine|first2=Fabien L.|last3=Kuch|first3=Melanie|last4=Enk|first4=Jacob|last5=Moraes-Barros|first5=Nadia|last6=Superina|first6=Mariella|last7=Poinar|first7=Hendrik N.|last8=Delsuc|first8=Frédéric|date=2016-03-01|title=Shotgun Mitogenomics Provides a Reference Phylogenetic Framework and Timescale for Living Xenarthrans|url=https://academic.oup.com/mbe/article/33/3/621/2579287|journal=Molecular Biology and Evolution|volume=33|issue=3|pages=621–642|doi=10.1093/molbev/msv250|issn=0737-4038|access-date=2018-03-18|archive-date=2018-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180604181140/https://academic.oup.com/mbe/article/33/3/621/2579287|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

